(1+x)^{n}=\sum\limits_{k=0}^{n}\binom{n}{k}x^k
\sum_{k=1}^{n}k^2\binom{n}{k}=\sum_{k=1}^{n}k^2\frac{n}{k}\binom{n-1}{k-1}
=\sum_{k=1}^{n}kn\binom{n-1}{k-1}=n\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}(k+1)\binom{n-1}{k}=
=n\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}k\binom{n-1}{k}+n\sum_{k=0}^{n-1}\binom{n-1}{k}=
=n\sum_{k=1}^{n-1}k\frac{n-1}{k}\binom{n-2}{k-1}+n2^{n-1}=
=n(n-1)\sum_{k=0}^{n-2}\binom{n-2}{k}+n2^{n-1}=
=n(n-1)2^{n-2}+2n2^{n-2}=n(n+1)2^{n-2}
